Actions.Text: AMEND AND RECOMMIT TO ENVIRONMENTAL CONSERVATION
AMEND AND RECOMMIT TO ENVIRONMENTAL CONSERVATION

Title: Relates to the disposition of certain fees and penalties
Summary: Provides for the disposition of certain fees and penalties; directs such fees to a conservation enforcement account in the state conservation fund.
LawCode: Amd En Con L, generally; amd ยง83, St Fin L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the environmental conservation law and the state finance law, in relation to the disposition of certain fees and penalties
